original_title: Bronx: McGraw Avenue - White Plains Road
text:
McGraw Avenue, east from White Plains Road (view 2). View 1 is east from Storrow Street and shows (left) the southern limit of the Catholic Protectory. View 2 shows the Metropolitan Life Insurance Company's Parkchester Houses under construction on the former Protectory grounds. McGraw Avenue is fenced off at Virginia Avenue.

P. L. Sperr
View 1: April 10, 1938
View 2: September 4, 1939
